(window["webpackJsonp"]=window["webpackJsonp"]||[]).push([["chunk-2d22d746"],{f820:function(e,a,t){"use strict";t.r(a);var o=t("7a23"),i={class:"blog-articles"},n=Object(o["o"])('<div class="blog-container"><header class="article-header"><h1 class="article-title" itemprop="name">About</h1><a target="_blank" rel="noopener external nofollow noreferrer" href="https://github.com/Blogjs/site/edit/master/source/about/index.md" class="article-edit-link" title="Improve this doc"><i class="fa fa-pencil"></i></a></header><div class="article-content" itemprop="articleBody"><p> Blog was originally created and maintained by <a target="_blank" rel="noopener external nofollow noreferrer" href="https://github.com/tommy351">Tommy Chen</a> in 2012. Since then, it has helped thousands of people to build their dream website/blog. </p><h2 id="Join-us" class="article-heading"><a href="#Join-us" class="headerlink" title="Join us"></a>Join us<a class="article-anchor" href="#Join-us" aria-hidden="true"></a></h2><p> We are the passionate people behind the Blog. If you would like to join Blog, you should have at least one approved PR. If you have already contributed to Blog, simply shot out an issue in any Blog repos. </p><p> If you have any question regarding joining Blog, feel free to contact the maintainer <a target="_blank" rel="noopener external nofollow noreferrer" href="https://github.com/NoahDragon">Abner Chou</a> or simply create an islogsue to ask. </p><h2 id="Contribute" class="article-heading"><a href="#Contribute" class="headerlink" title="Contribute"></a>Contribute<a class="article-anchor" href="#Contribute" aria-hidden="true"></a></h2><p> Don’t know where to start? Pick up any item in <a target="_blank" rel="noopener external nofollow noreferrer" href="https://github.com/Blogjs/Blog/issues/2492">Blog Roadmap</a>, and start from there. Don’t hesitate to ask questions, we are glad to help. </p><h2 id="Donate" class="article-heading"><a href="#Donate" class="headerlink" title="Donate"></a>Donate<a class="article-anchor" href="#Donate" aria-hidden="true"></a></h2><p><a target="_blank" rel="noopener external nofollow noreferrer" href="https://opencollective.com/Blog"><img src="https://opencollective.com/Blog/tiers/backers.svg?avatarHeight=60&amp;width=600" alt="Backers"></a></p><h4 id="Why" class="article-heading"><a href="#Why" class="headerlink" title="Why?"></a>Why?<a class="article-anchor" href="#Why" aria-hidden="true"></a></h4><p> First of all, many people have asked about donation, so here it is! </p><p> Second, in all good conscience, most of the visible costs (like the domain fees) are already covered by us. We also spend tremendous time to keep Blog running and functioning. This is the real cost and also invisible. </p><h4 id="Benefits" class="article-heading"><a href="#Benefits" class="headerlink" title="Benefits"></a>Benefits<a class="article-anchor" href="#Benefits" aria-hidden="true"></a></h4><p> We are grateful for every penny donated, here is a list of benefits you and us can achieve: </p><ol><li>Cover our cost.</li><li>Motivate and acknowledge our work.</li><li> List your name on Blog.io website (2.5k users and 10k pageviews per day!). </li></ol><p>There are two tiers of donation:</p><ul><li> Less than $100, your name and website link will be on the donor list. </li><li> More than $100, your name, icon, and website link will be on the home page for at least one month (depending on the amount). </li></ul><p>Again, thanks for your support!</p></div><footer class="article-footer"><time class="article-footer-updated" datetime="2022-07-23T22:02:36.296Z" itemprop="dateModified">Last updated: 2022-07-23</time></footer><section id="comments"><div id="disqus_thread"></div></section></div>',1),r=[n];function l(e,a,t,n,l,s){return Object(o["H"])(),Object(o["m"])("div",i,r)}var s={name:"Articles",props:{msg:String}};s.render=l;a["default"]=s}}]);